tip.text: Go on a jog here and take phenomenal photographs of the Golden Gate Bridge.
Go for a run when it's cold, foggy and cloudy because when that rare, sunny, warm day comes, you'll run the risk of tripping over people tanning, dogs running and kids playing.
Sit in the middle of the quad on a sunny day in the early afternoon and just watch the throngs of students light up the campus as they move from class to class.
